description: KinkMen Classics presents hot boy next door, Pierce Paris (Hartman) stepping onto the mat for the first time, going toe to toe with stud Kaden Alexander. Kaden is riding the high of winning his first victory and doesn’t plan on letting Pierce get in the way of that. Pierce may not have formal training, but with his superior size and extended reach, he plans on tangling up his opponent and giving him another devastating loss. Will the newcomer prove himself on the mat and completely humiliate his opponent? Or will he suffer a rough ground ‘n pound before getting a face full of thick cum?
title: Pierce Paris Challenges Kaden Alexander
